{"tid":223193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［情緒病撚入］想睇醫生","createTime":"2017-04-30T07:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T09:41:44.000Z","uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00636021fb0bdfad5ac989163a58709a2f2b75b3","tid":223193,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得自己有病好耐<br />\n之前屋企人都有叫過我去睇精神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家成個人都好攰 生存無乜意義咁<br />\n唔想自己再係咁煩到身邊嘅人<br />\n試過自殺都放棄咗 自殘都試過<br />\n但見到屋企人年紀老邁都唔想再打擾到佢地 想改變自己<br />\n<br />\n終於的起心肝想去睇醫生<br />\n但係無從入手<br />\n有無巴絲分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0ef4c8b197aa0d398e6078c395893bd00893aa","tid":223193,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"政府精神科免費"},{"pid":"162479c8dac09768ad08b4d4c6e232d5a65f16a8","tid":223193,"uid":48738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府精神科免費</blockquote><br />\n係咪要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194a9a07b9565333e395bb88c3613da533d98211","tid":223193,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府精神科免費</blockquote><br />\n係咪要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗街症先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e3e4863b69654ec9db9d911181b9df015e6afe","tid":223193,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政府精神科免費</blockquote><br />\n係咪要排好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咗街症先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"h